org.apache.juneau.utils

Class Mutable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.utils.Mutable<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The inner object type.

    public class Mutable<T>
extends Object
    Represents a settable object. Typically passed as method parameters to provide by-reference support.

    Mutable<String> m = Mutable.create(String.class); callSomeMethodThatSetsValue(m); String val = m.get();

    • This class is not thread safe.
    • This object can be used as hashmap keys.
